Sandra Mozarowsky https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sandra_Mozarowsky 0 Sandra Mozarowsky (17 October 1958 - 14 September 1977) was a Spanish actress. Her acting career started in 1969 and lasted until her death in 1977; she starred in films including La noche de las gaviotas (Night of the Seagulls), and Beatriz.
